{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/secret-agent-of-love-cinta-ditolak-agen-bertindak/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Secret Agent of Love: Cinta Ditolak, Agen Bertindak!","content":"\n<p>Punya masalah dengan hubungan asmara? Sedang bertengkar dengan pacar dan terancam putus? Jangan kuatir, karena di komik Secret Agent of Love, perusahaan Black Heart dengan senang hati akan membantu kamu!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54632\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/secret-agent-of-love-cinta-ditolak-agen-bertindak/attachment/01-secret-agent-of-love/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-secret-agent-of-love\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" alt=\"Seperti apakah organisasi Black Heart sebenarnya? Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54632\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-secret-agent-of-love.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Seperti apakah organisasi Black Heart sebenarnya? Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Black Heart merupakan perusahaan yang mampu memperbaiki\nhubungan asmara pasangan yang tengah dilanda musibah. Black Heart berbeda\ndengan perusahaan konseling asmara lain, karena Black Heart akan melakukan apa\nsaja untuk mewujudkan permintaan klien mereka. Salah satunya adalah dengan\nmemanipulasi situasi dan kondisi target mereka!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54633\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/secret-agent-of-love-cinta-ditolak-agen-bertindak/attachment/02-secret-agent-of-love/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-secret-agent-of-love\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" alt=\"Calista, anggota tim support Black Heart. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54633\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-secret-agent-of-love.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Calista, anggota tim support Black Heart. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Black Heart mengandalkan dua tim berbeda dalam operasinya.\nPertama ada tim support yang jadi timnya Calista. Tugas tim support adalah\nberhubungan langsung dengan klien untuk urusan operasional misi. Mereka\nmenyiapkan data dan informasi dari klien, dan memprosesnya menjadi intel\nberharga yang akan membantu misi para agen lapangan. Anggota tim support\nseperti Calista juga berkomunikasi dengan klien untuk mengabarkan perkembangan\nmisi serta meminta persetujuan klien untuk melaksanakan aksi-aksi tertentu.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54634\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/secret-agent-of-love-cinta-ditolak-agen-bertindak/attachment/03-secret-agent-of-love/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-secret-agent-of-love\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" alt=\"Agen X yang terjun ke lapangan. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54634\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-secret-agent-of-love.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Agen X yang terjun ke lapangan. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Bicara soal agen, para agen lapangan Black Heart menjadi\nberhubungan langsung dengan target yang diinginkan klien. Para agen seperti\nAgen X dan Agen Y memiliki kemampuan akting dan persuasi yang sangat hebat.\nMereka mampu membaca suasana hati target, serta beradaptasi dengan situasi dan\nkondisi yang tidak terduga. Mereka juga merupakan ahli penyamaran sehingga\nsosok aslinya tidak pernah diketahui. Ditambah intel dari tim support, para\nagen lapangan merupakan senjata paling berharga yang dimiliki Black Heart.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54635\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/secret-agent-of-love-cinta-ditolak-agen-bertindak/attachment/04-secret-agent-of-love/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-secret-agent-of-love\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" alt=\"Secret Agent of Love tampilkan berbagai macam skenario menarik. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54635\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-secret-agent-of-love.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Secret Agent of Love tampilkan berbagai macam skenario menarik. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Secret Agent of Love merupakan komik terbaru yang hadir di\nCIAYO Comics Plus+. Komik ini punya cerita yang dikarang oleh Revin Putra dan\nDhanie Ramadhan, yang kemudian diramu dalam naskah rancangan Rendi Datriansyah.\nIlustrasi komik ini dikerjakan oleh TRIARC STUDIO dengan finishing oleh Ilham\nRamdhani.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu suka nonton drama Korea mungkin bisa menemukan\nkesamaan antara Secret Agent of Love dengan serial Dating Agency Cyrano, namun\ndi komik ini kamu bisa mewujudkan fantasi agen rahasia yang membantu percintaan\norang lain. Kisah-kisah seperti ini sangat cocok buat kamu para hopeless\nromantic yang senang dengan berbagai jenis cerita cinta.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54636\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/secret-agent-of-love-cinta-ditolak-agen-bertindak/attachment/05-secret-agent-of-love/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-secret-agent-of-love\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" alt=\"Agen X menyamar untuk mengelabui targetnya. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54636\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-secret-agent-of-love.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Agen X menyamar untuk mengelabui targetnya. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu juga bisa berpartisipasi dalam komik Secret Agent of Love! Punya pacar yang sifatnya nyebelin, atau mau balas dendam sama mantan? Kamu bisa mengisi <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1RfdQHkczNVe5DfGZpq1Lkd4t4bH0NZJqDDf2czQg8rE/viewform?edit_requested=true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">form berikut ini</a> dengan informasi target, kelemahannya, serta siapa agen yang kamu inginkan untuk misi ini. Agen X atau Agen Y? Cukup isikan saja informasi yang dibutuhkan dan Calista akan mengurus sisanya.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54637\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/secret-agent-of-love-cinta-ditolak-agen-bertindak/attachment/06-secret-agent-of-love/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-secret-agent-of-love\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-secret-agent-of-love.jpg\" alt=\"Calista mencoba membujuk kliennya yang tengah galau. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54637\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-secret-agent-of-love.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-secret-agent-of-love-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Calista mencoba membujuk kliennya yang tengah galau. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ikuti terus sepak terjang Calista, Agen X, dan anggota Black Heart lainnya di komik Secret Agent of Love, setiap hari Sabtu pukul 19:00 WIB hanya di CIAYO Comics. Eh, tapi kok cuma ada season 1-nya aja? Itu artinya kamu haru gabung dengan <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/segera-update-ciayo-comics-plus/\" target=\"_blank\">CIAYO Comics Plus+</a>! Hanya dengan 15 ribu Rupiah per bulannya, kamu bisa membaca berbagai <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/8-komik-eksklusif-ciayo-comics-plus-yang-harus-kamu-ikutin/\" target=\"_blank\">komik eksklusif</a>, baca chapter komik favorit lebih cepat dari yang lain, dan <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/plus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">berbagai fitur lainnya</a>!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"e0b4a884-c0af-5078-ace2-ccbcbd7a16d5"}}}